<h2>
  Welcome to the Memecoop Alpha!
</h2>

<p>
Memecoop is a platform for discussing ideas. We're just getting started, but you're more than
welcome to play with what we've got so far. For now it will look a lot like the comment threads or
forums you're used to, but over the coming months we'll be steadily adding functionality.
</p>

<p>
To get started:
</p>

<ul>
  <% unless current_user %>
    <li><%= link_to "Use Facebook", "/auth/facebook" %> to login.</li>
  <% end %>
  <% if permitted_to? :read, Topic.new %>
    <li>Browse <%= link_to "current topics", topics_path %>.</li>
  <% end %>
  <% if permitted_to? :create, Topic.new %>
    <li>Start a <%= link_to "new topic", new_topic_path %>.</li>
  <% end %>
</ul>
